may go even beyond one =\r\ncycle of creation. Else why would Krshna and Arjuna fight the very same ene=\r\nmies that they had been fighting in the past cycle of creation? Mahabharata=\r\n says\n so. I believe it. \n\n\n\nWhat then is the final aim of all this, spirit=\r\nuality etc? I don&#39;t know. Maybe, to teach us to broaden our perspectives an=\r\nd consequentially lessen our attachments to our otherwise mundane lives and=\r\n its mundane problems. This is like a circular roller-coaster ride we see i=\r\nn local melas. Tighten the seat-belts, bring a smile in the heart, be detac=\r\nhed and enjoy the show! \n\n\nBest of luck and take good care of yourself! \n\n\n=\r\n-Regards \n=C2=A0Rajarshi \n\n\n\nawaktam wyaktimApannam manyantE mAmabuddhayah =\r\n| \nparam bhAwamajAnanto mamAwyayamanuttamam ||[7:24] \n\n\n___________________=\r\n________________\n\nFrom: Laxmi Narayan &lt;shrijishrihari@...&gt; \nTo: &quot;ve=\r\ndic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com&quot;=C2=A0 &lt;vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com&gt; \nSent: Sat=\r\nurday, 28 July 2012 7:30 PM \nSubject: Re: [vedic-wisdom] To those who say t=\r\nhat they don=E2=80=99t believe in any religion \n\n=C2=A0 Dear Rajarshi Bhai,=\r\n \nHow are you? You have to complete the story. you have to tell what happen=\r\ned when X went to meet this man in temple.or anything else which happened. =\r\nIt is like somebody gone in kitchen to get rest of meal and not come back. =\r\n\n\n\nFirst I have to thank you for writing that story about Divine Mother Sri=\r\n Chinnmastaji. I had developed a fear about Her but 3 times I got spiritual=\r\n indications over the period of 2 months that I should write my story. When=\r\n you wrote back suddenly my fear about Her melted away and I did immediate =\r\nprayers to Her. Thanks. \n\n\nThe other thing is can I dare to say that I do n=\r\not agree what is in this thread. Why does this so called spiritual man has =\r\nto dump his failure on=C2=A0 religion. If people do not believe in religion=\r\n